                    <span>This was a very quick read for me. I was done in a couple hours. Anybody curious about Chuck Zito or interested in the Hells Angels should read it. There's a fair amount of chest pounding, but a lot of reality, too.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The REAL Rocky Balboa...</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
